  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/a5274b35601cc518636248dcf4a8442c.avif?t=1750768175\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras_big/a5274b35601cc518636248dcf4a8442c.avif?t=1750768175 width=800 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The year is 2142, and New Earth is buzzing with excitement as the prestigious Universe Space Jumper Championship begins. You, a rookie competitor, must face off against the galaxy’s most skilled Space Jumpers. With high stakes and the weight of the universe on your shoulders, you must jump through warp tunnels to prove yourself, earn your glory, and become a symbol of hope for humanity’s future.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/7c1aceb35478c9f188345e75f292c463.poster.avif?t=1750768175\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/7c1aceb35478c9f188345e75f292c463.webm?t=1750768175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/7c1aceb35478c9f188345e75f292c463.mp4?t=1750768175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/0b380098e804701b545839fca61a1347.avif?t=1750768175\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras_big/0b380098e804701b545839fca61a1347.avif?t=1750768175 width=800 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the fast-paced action of Space Drop. Each level presents an adrenaline-pumping sequence in which you fly through warp tunnels while dodging obstacles, collecting power-ups, shooting down asteroids, and much more. With a vast variety of levels to conquer, each with its own difficulty - every jump becomes a true test of your skill and reflexes. Perfect for those craving fun, fast-paced VR action!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/7da1cb2be2ae12b04f3772128c6c7eaf.poster.avif?t=1750768175\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/7da1cb2be2ae12b04f3772128c6c7eaf.webm?t=1750768175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/7da1cb2be2ae12b04f3772128c6c7eaf.mp4?t=1750768175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/7e8b830f1deab138d949e75ccf589f95.avif?t=1750768175\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras_big/7e8b830f1deab138d949e75ccf589f95.avif?t=1750768175 width=800 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Power-ups are key to your survival in Space Drop. Get more shields to recover after hitting obstacles, grab an invincibility pickup for those critical last-second moments, snatch some energy for more ammunition, and gravitate to the nearest points pickup for more score. Learning how to use these power-ups effectively is essential to dominate the leaderboards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/cecc1ec7baace9a696706df1c2701bcc.poster.avif?t=1750768175\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/cecc1ec7baace9a696706df1c2701bcc.webm?t=1750768175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/cecc1ec7baace9a696706df1c2701bcc.mp4?t=1750768175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/d7ca4ac7a73eb6afc2190dbdc5aa86cb.avif?t=1750768175\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras_big/d7ca4ac7a73eb6afc2190dbdc5aa86cb.avif?t=1750768175 width=800 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience endless replayability with our custom level generator. Tweak a variety of different settings to create your own unique warp tunnels filled with exciting challenges to overcome. Whether you want to create easier levels to slow down the pace, or test your limits with even harder ones - the choice is entirely yours to make.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/9f0ab37099f6ccca6d96b7a1438f44f1.poster.avif?t=1750768175\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/9f0ab37099f6ccca6d96b7a1438f44f1.webm?t=1750768175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/9f0ab37099f6ccca6d96b7a1438f44f1.mp4?t=1750768175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/91e8ebeb242f2ad05f0b36b34790138b.avif?t=1750768175\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras_big/91e8ebeb242f2ad05f0b36b34790138b.avif?t=1750768175 width=800 height=41 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Leap from spaceships into warp tunnels in VR</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Fly through space at breakneck speeds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Shoot your way through obstacles with your blasters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Collect pickups to adapt your playstyle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Customize levels with our expansive level generator</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Earn score to top the leaderboards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Experience a unique soundtrack as you soar through space</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/a5274b35601cc518636248dcf4a8442c.avif?t=1750768175\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras_big/a5274b35601cc518636248dcf4a8442c.avif?t=1750768175 width=800 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The year is 2142, and New Earth is buzzing with excitement as the prestigious Universe Space Jumper Championship begins. You, a rookie competitor, must face off against the galaxy’s most skilled Space Jumpers. With high stakes and the weight of the universe on your shoulders, you must jump through warp tunnels to prove yourself, earn your glory, and become a symbol of hope for humanity’s future.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/7c1aceb35478c9f188345e75f292c463.poster.avif?t=1750768175\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/7c1aceb35478c9f188345e75f292c463.webm?t=1750768175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/7c1aceb35478c9f188345e75f292c463.mp4?t=1750768175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras/0b380098e804701b545839fca61a1347.avif?t=1750768175\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2605140/extras_big/0b380098e804701b545839fca61a1347.avif?t=1750768175 width=800 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience 